{"tid":1830030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我的網誌- 花市行 - 行政長官","createTime":"2020-01-19T09:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T09:38:08.000Z","uid":5469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b670d520222b0c30dd19d2dae15c71e272465237","tid":1830030,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"雖然近日香港天氣寒冷，但無損市民一家大小、扶老攜幼逛花市的興致。我今日下午亦和太太到沙田年宵市場買花過年。<br />\n<br />\n今年香港冬季氣候變化大，一月上旬天氣和暖，但下旬氣溫急降，更錄得五十九年來最低溫度，新界部分地方出現凍雨和結霜。年宵市場的花農跟我說，年花的品質和花時都受影響，擔心銷情未如理想。我自己喜愛種植，完全理解務農的艱辛。年花是花農一年的心血，希望大家多多支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ceo.gov.hk/archive/2017/chi/blog/blog20160205.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceo.gov.hk%2Farchive%2F2017%2Fchi%2Fblog%2Fblog20160205.html&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=ee116265\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ceo.gov.hk/archive/2017/chi/blog/blog20160205.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲今晚凍凍地，想行花市？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ab5604bd7b8522ca729bda62dc7f17ea2bbaa5","tid":1830030,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家出面警暴橫行，<br />\n你哋班冷氣撚仲係度施施然睇live?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同我上twitter做國際戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經唔駛你行，撳掣打字都唔得？<br />\n入 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=ed48b5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task1</span></span> 接任務</span><br />\n－－－<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nbcchicago/status/1218816043507908609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnbcchicago%2Fstatus%2F1218816043507908609&d=3W